      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 2,
      "text": "Incident",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 3,
      "text": "9 September 1947",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 4,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 5,
      "text": "MEMORANDUM FOR THE OFFICER IN CHARGE:",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 6,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "text": "[REDACTED] Berkeley, California, was",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "text": "interviewed 9 September 1947 at his place of employment, the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "text": "[REDACTED] University of California, concerning flying objects he reported",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "text": "to have seen on 29 July 1947 while with [REDACTED] of the",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "415th AAF BU (RT). [REDACTED] stated in substance that he was a 1st Lt",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "in the Reserve and that on the 29th of July 1947 shortly after 12 noon he",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "and [REDACTED] had just landed from a routine training flight when",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "[REDACTED] called [REDACTED] attention to an unidentified flying",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "object that was following a P-80 aircraft at a terrific rate of speed.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "[REDACTED] estimated the P-80 to be flying at approximately 250 miles",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "per hour on a preliminary approach to landing at Hamilton Field. In",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "[REDACTED] estimation the object he saw following the P-80 maintained a",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "speed of three to four times that of the aircraft. A moment later a",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "second object appeared and flew a course described as something similar",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "to a fighter aircraft's maneuvers when accompanying heavier ships, or a",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "left to right movement, over the object first sighted. [REDACTED] stated",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "that this maneuvering continued until the objects were out of sight. He",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "estimated the time to be approximately 15 seconds, the course approximately",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "120 degrees. [REDACTED] could not estimate the size of the objects nor",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "actual altitude, though he did not believe them to be beyond six thousand",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "feet. [REDACTED] described the objects as being milky white in color,",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "and unlike any conventional type aircraft he had ever seen. When questioned",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "whether he was familiar with the Navy \"Flapjack\", [REDACTED] stated that",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "he was, and that he was certain the objects he reported seeing were not of",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "this nature.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "AGENT'S NOTES: [REDACTED] is a former officer of the U.S. AAF and a B-29",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "pilot of considerable experience. [REDACTED] does not convey the im-",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "pression of being the kind of person who would \"imagine\" that he was seeing",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "text": "objects, nor has he any apparent desire for publicity. [REDACTED] is in",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "charge of [REDACTED] Berkeley, California.",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "status": "blank"
    },
